        ["Customer Satisfaction", "Deliver excellent value and service", "Service-oriented businesses", "Air Peace Airlines focused on punctuality and customer experience"],
        ["Environmental Sustainability", "Reduce environmental impact", "Firms under regulatory or public scrutiny", "Dangote Refinery investing in cleaner production technology"]
