        ["Selective Perception", "Receiver interprets messages through personal bias", "An employee who distrusts management may interpret a cost-cutting memo as a precursor to retrenchment", "Communicate context and reasoning clearly; address rumours proactively"],
        ["Technological Barriers", "Outdated equipment, poor connectivity, system failures", "Frequent power cuts disrupt video calls and internet-based communication across many Nigerian offices", "Invest in backup systems; use asynchronous communication (email, recorded videos)"]
